reviewText: No music on this DVD. And FYI it's unauthorized, as stated on the cover.
If you're a die hard Ed Sheeran fan such as myself you probably will be disappointed in this. YouTube offers more for free.

Not sure why people are leaving 1 star reviews complaining about the lack of music, when it clearly says this is a documentary about his life, not a concert DVD. If you want live music, order Live at Wembley.
Not at all what I expected it to be.  No music at all.

To Live Music sounded like he was singing live on DVD, but it was only interviews and it sucks. Should have returned it!!! I cannot submit zero stars, so I am putting one star. But, it doesn't even deserve one star.
This is the 2nd dvd I have bought in the last 2 months.  No where did I read that it was an interview...again!  I just want a Ed Sheeran music dvd for our outdoor movie theater. So disappointing. :(
